title: No. 4 Tech on wrong end of wild ending in Ft. Worth - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 4 Tech on wrong end of wild ending in Ft. Worth - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: FORT WORTH, Texas – No. 4 Texas Tech rallied late, but came up short against TCU, falling 4-3 on Friday night at Lupton Stadium. The Red Raiders trailed 4-0 before scoring two in the eighth and one in the ninth.
